{"article_id":"qocgzGJ0gjRfpECe","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Outgoing Sen. Jeff Flake","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"( R-AZ )","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"is not going to leave quietly into the night .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"He ' s continuing his role as the GOP ' s biggest pain in the a * *","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"by declaring","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"he will block further judicial nominations","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"until the Senate brings up legislation","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to protect Special Counsel Robert Mueller .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"With Jeff Sessions being fired as attorney general ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Matt Whitaker has become the acting chief at the Justice Department .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Whitaker has slammed the Mueller probe ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"which is looking into whether the Trump campaign colluded with the Russians during the 2016 election ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"and has declared","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"he has no intention of recusing himself .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"He ' s in a position","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"to oversee the investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"which has given congressional Democrats an ample amount of heartburn .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"There have been calls for special legislation to be passed","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to protect Mueller and the investigation from Democrats .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Flake has decided to assume the role of Benedict Arnold again .","depth":3},{"id":20,"text":"With Flake being the deciding vote on the Senate Judiciary Committee ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"the gentleman from Arizona has made himself an obstacle...again","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"( via The Hill ) :","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Sen. Jeff Flake","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"( R-Ariz. )","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"said on Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"that he will oppose any of President Trump 's judicial nominations","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"until legislation","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"protecting special counsel Robert Mueller","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"gets a vote .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"`` I have informed the majority leader","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"I will not vote to advance any of the 21 judicial nominees","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"pending in the Judiciary Committee","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"or vote to confirm the 32 judges","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"awaiting confirmation on the Senate floor","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"until ... [ the bill ] is brought to the full Senate for a vote , ''","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Flake said from the Senate floor .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Flake 's threat will block the Judiciary Committee from approving judicial nominations","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"and sending them to the full Senate","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"without help from Democrats .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Republicans hold a 11-10 majority on the panel","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"and many of the most controversial nominees pass along party lines ,","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"meaning they would need either Flake 's vote or a Democratic senator","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"to flip .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"On the Senate floor , Majority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"( R-Ky. )","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"has slightly more leeway .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"With a 51-49 majority , Flake would need a Republican colleague to join him and every Democrat","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"to block a judicial nominee on the Senate floor . .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"@ JeffFlake announces on the floor","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"he has informed McConnell","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"he will not for any judicial nominees on the floor or in the Judiciary Committee","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"until the Mueller protection bill gets a floor vote","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"- Phil Mattingly","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"( @ Phil_Mattingly )","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"November 14 , 2018","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Flake :","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"`` I have informed the Majority Leader","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"that I will not vote to advance any of the 21 judicial nominees","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"pending in the Judiciary Committee ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"or vote to confirm the 32 judges","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"awaiting a confirmation vote on the floor ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"until S. 2644 is brought to the full Senate for a vote . ''","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"- Phil Mattingly","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"( @ Phil_Mattingly )","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"November 14 , 2018","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"NEW :","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"@ JeffFlake says","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"he will not vote to advance any of of the 21 judicial nominees","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"pending in the judicial committee ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"or vote to confirm the 32 judges","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"awaiting confirmation on the Senate floor","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"until the Mueller protection bill is brought up for a full vote on the Senate floor .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"- Frank Thorp V","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"( @ frankthorp )","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"November 14 , 2018","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"Flake had threatened to hold up judicial nominees in June as bargaining chips in the debate over Trump ' s position of tariffs and travel restrictions to Cuba .","depth":3},{"id":77,"text":"This man ca n't leave Washington soon enough .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":155,"left":117,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":96,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":80,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":79,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":79,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"